{"tid":601084,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗點名5位青年球員 未來會震撼球壇","createTime":"2018-03-22T02:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T17:55:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":28,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b5453a10f09b1bf81989aff12f916ebab66c46","tid":601084,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:22:32.000Z","msg":"Tip五個衰三個 C朗成新一代「燈神」？<br />\n<br />\n C朗當時第一個點名嘅就係有挪威神童之稱嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">馬田奧迪加特</span>：「我見到而家好多年青球員嘅技術都好出眾，就好似奧迪加特咁，佢只有16歲，但已經好出色。」不過奧迪加特經過三年後只係喺皇馬一隊上陣過兩次，今季仲被借咗去海倫芬。<br />\n<br />\n其餘四位有被C朗「欽點」嘅仲有前曼聯翼鋒<span style=\"color: red;\">迪比、夏薩特、保羅普巴同埋尼馬</span>，不過除咗夏薩特同尼馬之外，其他三位球員近年嘅發展同表現似乎都只係一般，睇嚟C朗嘅「燈力」同比利都不相伯仲。"},{"pid":"58a7bf0b6d33b9e396265bffc66fc0f4d26c3670","tid":601084,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:29:31.000Z","msg":"又反普巴"},{"pid":"69f48fe2bbe2073663e148aa287626138dfd2bbf","tid":601084,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b3726ace12fb843e4d80b7b830c511eb9a80d26","tid":601084,"uid":107927,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"奧迪加特...太細個去皇馬真係嘥晒"},{"pid":"c1739822ed8955883563fe90110fc696236eb78d","tid":601084,"uid":130118,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5b3726ace12fb843e4d80b7b830c511eb9a80d26","tid":601084,"uid":107927,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"奧迪加特...太細個去皇馬真係嘥晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"疤個哈利路域都吹到當年上天<br />\n已家又係踼唔起"},{"pid":"5405708d0241f2f4fa7b7f7c498006f2a6ad334e","tid":601084,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"當時姐係幾時？"},{"pid":"f1f10bc98e568f819e1c05ac0dac45e02c500e47","tid":601084,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T02:48:31.000Z","msg":"Nigger6 只會同巴洛迪利一樣"},{"pid":"3c1ed6cb6c46f91e